==== Easy caching DNS ====

{{RootCmd|echo 'dns_servers{{=}}"127.0.0.1"' >> /etc/conf.d/net}}

As root edit {{Path|/etc/bind/named.conf}} add an internet service provider's DNS where the x.x.x.x are.

{{FileBox|filename=/etc/bind/named.conf|1=
	forwarders {
		x.x.x.x;	// Your ISP NS
		x.x.x.x;	// Your ISP NS
		4.2.2.1;		// Level3 Public DNS
		4.2.2.2;		// Level3 Public DNS
		8.8.4.4;		// Google Open DNS
		8.8.8.8;		// Google Open DNS
	};
}}

